BUG-032 demo flag.

Created so that on the first main-loop tick after this PR lands and
the trader restarts, an hourly summary fires immediately (bypassing
the per-hour dedup marker). The trader consumes the flag after a
successful dispatch — see src/main.py.

Operator: if you don't see a summary in Telegram within ~15 minutes
(one tick interval) after restart, run:

    PYTHONPATH=. python scripts/send_hourly_now.py

on the VM, or `/hourly` from Telegram, and watch
`journalctl -u ict-trader-live -f` for `hourly_report → dispatched`.
